description:
This is a 18 minute workout called 'Senior & Beginner Workout - 15 minute Gentle Chair Yoga' from the channel SeniorShape Fitness.
The workout falls under Flexibility/Yoga and Flexibility/Stretching.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
You'll need Other for this workout.
The workout has a The Comfort Moves and The Reboot Workout vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Light.

Original workout description: Stand taller and join me in this great 15 minute chair yoga workout. This is a perfect routine if you are uncomfortable getting on the floor. The stretches included in this workout are appropriate for anyone and  also serve as a good stretch break if you sit at your desk all day.

Grab a chair, relax and find your breath as we gently stretch our shoulders, chest, triceps, glutes, thighs and back. 

Enjoy and please subscribe to SeniorShape!
